        <item>
            <title>WhatsApp 動態將可加入音樂，方便分享自己正在聽的音樂</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/add-music-to-your-whatsapp-status/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=add-music-to-your-whatsapp-status</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/add-music-to-your-whatsapp-status/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 14:00:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[WhatsApp]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300239</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>從前在即時通訊軟件例如 MSN Messenger 上，可以顯示自己正在播放的音樂，而 Meta 最近也吹懷舊風，繼 Instagram 之後，在 WhatsApp 上也加入類似的功能。<br /><span id="more-1300239"></span></p><p>WhatsApp 這個新功能讓用户可以在個人動態中加入音樂片段，將會陸續向全球用户開放。WhatsApp 的狀態功能位於更新標籤中，可用於分享類似於 Facebook 和 Instagram 上 Stories 功能的文字、照片和影片訊息，這些內容會在 24 小時後消失。當用户選擇新增動態時，螢幕頂部現在會出現一個音符圖標，選擇後可以加入音樂，照片最多 15 秒，影片最多 60 秒。</p><p>WhatsApp 表示，其音樂庫中有「數百萬首歌曲可供選擇」，用户可以選擇歌曲的特定部分加入到動態中。WhatsApp 上的動態像訊息一樣，採用端對端加密，WhatsApp 表示，他們無法看到用户分享的內容，也不會知道哪些歌曲被加入到動態中。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://blog.whatsapp.com/add-music-to-your-whatsapp-status">WhatsApp</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/add-music-to-your-whatsapp-status/life-tech/social-network/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Windows 11 安裝避開登入 Microsoft 帳户變困難，人氣設定漏洞被封鎖</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/microsoft-will-force-windows-11-installs-to-use-a-microsoft-account/software/windows-11/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-will-force-windows-11-installs-to-use-a-microsoft-account</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/microsoft-will-force-windows-11-installs-to-use-a-microsoft-account/software/windows-11/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 13:00:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Windows 11]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300202</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>雖然 Windows 11 在安裝的時候會要求用户登入 Microsoft 帳户，但不少用户因為各種原因並不希望連結 Microsoft 帳户，其中一個常見方法就是使用 bypassnro 指令。不過這個「漏洞」最近就在新的測試版中被封鎖。<br /><span id="more-1300202"></span></p><p>當 Windows 11 版本 22H2 發布時，Microsoft 就曾經要求 Windows 11 Home 和 Windows 11 Pro 在安裝過程中都需要互聯網連接和 Microsoft 帳户，但很快就有人發現繞過此要求的方法。最常用的繞過方法是輸入命令「bypassnro」，當在 Windows 安裝過程中在命令提示符中輸入此命令時，可以跳過連接互聯網，從而繞過 Microsoft 帳户要求。</p><p>不過最新的 Windows 11 預覽版就註明，Microsoft 正在移除此命令以「確保所有用户在完成設定時都具有互聯網連接和 Microsoft 帳户」。已經在沒有 Microsoft 帳户的情況下設定的 Windows 11 電腦不會受到影響。此變更只會影響 Windows 11 安裝和設定體驗。</p><p>這變更引起了一些爭議，特別是那些不希望在 Windows 11 上使用 Microsoft 帳户的用户對此就感到不滿。目前仍有其他方式可以繞過這些要求，包括設定自動化 unattend.xml 安裝，這可以跳過設定階段，但就比較麻煩，例如需要從頭開始建立新的 Windows 安裝映像等。而這些方式可能在未來也會被 Microsoft 封鎖，來確保 Windows 11 安裝時已經連接到 Microsoft 帳户。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.windowscentral.com/software-apps/windows-11/microsoft-will-force-windows-11-installs-to-use-a-microsoft-account-confirms-removal-of-popular-setup-bypass">Windows Central</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/microsoft-will-force-windows-11-installs-to-use-a-microsoft-account/software/windows-11/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Sony 建立 PlayStation Studios 保險庫，備份保存 30 年遊戲開發歷史</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/30-years-of-history-reside-in-our-tape-backups/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=30-years-of-history-reside-in-our-tape-backups</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/30-years-of-history-reside-in-our-tape-backups/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 12:00:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[playstation]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300191</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>雖然現在網絡發達，要找資料好像很容易，但其實很多珍貴的數據消失了就很難尋回。Sony 近年就設立了遊戲開發保險庫，把旗下工作室的遊戲開發相關素材和資料收藏，以便未來作為參考。<br /><span id="more-1300191"></span></p><p>Sony 在 2022 年的時候聘請了 Garrett Fredley 加入當時新成立的保存團隊，致力於尋找和保存 PlayStation 30 年歷史的相關文獻。近日，Fredley 在遊戲開發者大會（GDC）上發表演講，分享團隊工作進展，表示最近已經成立了「PlayStation Studios Vault」（PlayStation 工作室保險庫），用以儲存有關 Sony 遊戲製作歷史的一切資料。</p><p>保險庫現在存放遊戲構建檔案、原始碼和原始藝術作品，還有各種其他檔案。Fredley 解釋，建立保險庫的目的是保存「與遊戲項目相關的一切可能找到的東西：從文件到音頻資產，再到原型資訊，任何可能的東西，甚至文化文物。」如果與 PlayStation 工作室遊戲有關，團隊都會將其儲存在保險庫中，甚至包括製作遊戲的開發團隊照片。目前，團隊收藏中最古老的項目有 1994 年的時間戳，來自戰術角色扮演遊戲《Arc the Lad》。</p><p>保險庫目前有兩個主要伺服器，分別位於美國內華達州拉斯維加斯和英國利物浦，存儲著 650 TB 的數據，約 2 億個檔案。這幾乎是 Fredley 去年在另一次演講中提到的團隊收集的 350 TB 數據的兩倍。他預計將很快超過團隊目前設置可處理的 1 PB 雲端伺服器存儲數據，特別是隨著越來越多遊戲的開發。保存團隊使用工具協助工作，包括一個名為 Vaultron 的機器人，可以讀取數千張光碟來尋找檔案。但工作仍然不容易，因為大多數工作室並不會以便於數十年後理解和存取的方式儲存檔案。未來 Fredley 和他的團隊將需要解決幾個預期會出現的問題，例如需要良好的索引工具，並找出維持使用所收集檔案能力的方法。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/games/30-years-of-history-reside-in-our-tape-backups-playstations-building-a-game-preservation-mineshaft-vault-with-200-million-files-going-back-to-a-1994-build-of-ps1-jrpg-arc-the-lad/">GamesRadar+</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/30-years-of-history-reside-in-our-tape-backups/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>日本開發核廢料再利用技術，貧鈾可轉化為充電池使用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/first-assembly-of-a-uranium-based-rechargeable-battery/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=first-assembly-of-a-uranium-based-rechargeable-battery</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/first-assembly-of-a-uranium-based-rechargeable-battery/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 11:00:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[日本]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[核能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300187</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本原子能機構 (JAEA) 成功開發出世界首個「鈾充電電池」，利用鈾的獨特化學特性實現實用化，並已驗證其充放電性能。鈾長期以來被視為化學電池活性材料的候選者，此研究首次將其理論潛力轉化為實際應用，為可再生能源領域帶來新的儲能選擇。<br /><span id="more-1300187"></span></p><p>核燃料生產過程中會產生副產品「貧鈾」。由於貧化鈾無法在核反應堆（輕水反應堆）中用作燃料，又不能隨便棄置，只可以封存起來，例如日本目前就封存了約 16,000 噸貧化鈾。為了將貧鈾作為新資源利用，2000 年代初期就已經提出了使用鈾作為活性材料的充電電池概念，但此前未有研究報告組裝的鈾充電電池的具體性能。</p><p>JAEA 研究團隊開發的鈾充電電池使用鈾作為負極活性材料，鐵作為正極。原型電池單電池電壓為 1.3 伏，接近普通鹼性電池（1.5 伏）。電池經過 10 次充放電測試，性能幾乎沒有變化，表現出相對穩定的循環特性。團隊目前正在開發更高容量的流動電池（氧化還原流電池）和電解質循環系統，希望可以達致實際應用。</p><p>近年來，隨著可再生能源的引入增加，對充電電池的需求也在增長。太陽能、風能等發電受天氣條件影響，具有發電波動不穩定的特點。在這種情況下，通過充電電池等儲能裝置進行輸出控制是必要的，新儲能技術的開發正受到關注。若鈾充電電池增加容量並投入實際使用，日本儲存的大量貧鈾將成為可再生能源電力供應網絡輸出控制的新資源，有助於實現脱碳社會。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.jaea.go.jp/english/news/press/2025/031301/">JAEA</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/first-assembly-of-a-uranium-based-rechargeable-battery/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>MG 高達維度爾 + HG 白騎士開箱</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/mgvidar/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mgvidar</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/mgvidar/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:20:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300221</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<h2>MG 高達維度爾</h2><p>MG 高達維度爾 ASW-G-XX Gundam Vidar，是屬於《機動戰士高達，鐵血的孤兒》第二季的機體，現已推出，立即為大家開箱看看。在動畫中，高達維度爾由蓋利歐·鮑德温（Gaelio Bauduin）駕駛，該角色採用「維度爾」作為化名，象徵北歐神話中的復仇之神。其原型為受損的高達基馬利斯（Gundam Kimaris Trooper），在月球外軌道聯合艦隊（Arianrhod Fleet）的改裝下，成為具備更高戰鬥力的機體。設計師形部一平參與了機體的監修，確保模型與動畫設定一致。</p><p><a title="_DSC9084" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218954/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218954_009b5c7253_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9084" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ezgif85b0a748dd7376.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="513" /></p><p>模型的高達框架有修改過，肩關節的活動範圍顯著提升，適合模擬動畫中的戰鬥姿勢。腳部的獵刃可展開，增加機動感的視覺效果，而膝部裝甲與推進器的同步移動確保了腿部彎曲時的流暢性與真實感。手槍的 blowback movement 是 MG 系列的可動機構設計，而步槍的彈匣可拆卸，允許玩家模擬裝填或更換彈藥的場景。突擊軍刀則配有可替換的刀刃零件，能重現動畫中脱離刀鞘的狀態，細節精緻。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9086" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270258/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270258_1ebb8acd4b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9086" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9088" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418161872/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418161872_b70934e9f6_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9088" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9087" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419024971/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419024971_34be9e8484_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9087" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9089" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218889/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218889_97e21b7cb4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9089" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9090" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414280/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414280_23230d9573_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9090" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9093" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418161852/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418161852_052d0e402b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9093" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9094" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414265/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414265_84afff3025_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9094" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9095" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419024896/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419024896_cc9a54d34f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9095" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9096" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218834/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218834_5d34219373_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9096" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9085" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270228/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270228_0553df4234_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9085" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9097" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414255/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414255_0c06b1ce67_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9097" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9098" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218819/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218819_26f10320e4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9098" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9099" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218824/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218824_805cdb5b6d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9099" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9100" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270108/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270108_4ac8d3c142_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9100" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>駕駛艙的阿賴耶識 Type-E 特色系統，模型允許玩家選擇顯示啟動或關閉狀態，反映了機體在戰鬥中的不同模式。這一設計不僅增加了收藏價值，也讓玩家能更深入體驗動畫設定。除了武器與零件，模型還包括兩款蓋利歐·鮑德温的人偶，站姿與坐姿各一，適合用於駕駛艙內或獨立展示。</p><p>參考售價：6,600 日圓（含税）</p><h2>官方完成圖</h2><h2><a title="172481064359_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419233984/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419233984_b0b9945a61_b.jpg" alt="172481064359_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064478_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419039831/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419039831_162ed7d8ae_b.jpg" alt="172481064478_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064540_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419233959/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419233959_28dd86061c_b.jpg" alt="172481064540_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064651_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285508/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285508_1c165685a6_b.jpg" alt="172481064651_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064723_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418176772/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418176772_919551e02b_b.jpg" alt="172481064723_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064888_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285518/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285518_78e94ab6e6_b.jpg" alt="172481064888_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064950_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285513/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285513_13cb4bf76b_b.jpg" alt="172481064950_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></h2><h2><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">HG 白騎士 Weissritter</span></span></h2><p>HG 機戰 OG 系列繼續有新作推出，今次是白騎士 Weissritter PTX-007-03C，隸屬 ATX 計畫，由艾克瑟蓮·白朗寧駕駛，以「亡靈 Mk-II・T 型」為基礎改造而成，專為遠程砲戰設計。它搭載特斯拉飛行裝置，實現人形姿態單獨飛行，機動性極高，但裝甲輕量化導致防禦力較弱，適合搭配南部響介的「古鐵」進行後方支援，亦是小編最愛之一的機體。武器包括威力強大的「騎槍重砲」、三連裝光束加農砲和電漿刀，戰術多樣化。</p><p><a title="_DSC9102" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414420/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414420_2803c31396_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9102" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9104" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270383/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270383_33da90eb0d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9104" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9105" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270373/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270373_ebddea3430_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9105" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC9107" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270338/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270338_5f0af1d89f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9107" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9108" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419219054/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419219054_b918d6bbf0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9108" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9109" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419219014/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419219014_c3c2837583_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9109" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此 HG 模型依據動畫版大張正己風格設計，融入設計師齊藤和衞的原始設定，造型優雅且細節豐富。模型採用多軸關節，肩部、頸部和腰部靈活可動，能擺出雙手持槍的帥氣姿勢。配件包含騎槍重砲、三連裝光束加農砲、電漿刀、手掌零件及可動展示架，並附貼紙補色。白藍配色與透明綠雙眼零件還原經典形象，完成後高度約 15cm。</p><p><a title="_DSC9106" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418162002/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418162002_a6b86c21fa_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9106" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9110" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218999/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218999_dd662e0780_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9110" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9111" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270348/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270348_43997a9af2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9111" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9112" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414385/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414385_40de4f34f4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9112" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>參考售價：4,950 日圓（含税)</p><h2>官方完成圖</h2><p><a title="172863525250_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418210742/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418210742_aafc7e3224_b.jpg" alt="172863525250_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="172863524771_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418210762/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418210762_93987f4307_b.jpg" alt="172863524771_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172863524835_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419319983/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419319983_1e573c7e04_b.jpg" alt="172863524835_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172863524954_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419074126/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419074126_888721d772_b.jpg" alt="172863524954_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172863525055_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419319958/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419319958_caa617965a_b.jpg" alt="172863525055_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/mgvidar/fun-tech/">MG 高達維度爾 + HG 白騎士開箱</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
